properties.Name: ExperianConsumerSpouseCoApplicant
properties.Description:
Guarantors, also called cosigners, co-applicant, or joint account holders have the same responsibility with regard to the debt. C

Cosigners and joint account holders are both equally responsible for repayment of the debt. Therefore, the account would appear on both the primary account holder's and co-applicant's credit report.
